      "bookmarkId": "3300124528_15_8979-9058",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "8979-9058",
      "markText": "通常而言，可以将风险投资划分为天使及种子期、初创期、成长期、成熟期4个阶段，投早投小的天使及种子期、初创期的风投占比越高，通常意味着风投整体的风险偏好也越高。",
      "totalCount": 2170,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300124528&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=8979&rangeEnd=9058",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/96632b50813ab9724g018e30?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=8979&rangeEnd=9058"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300124528_11_7907-7964",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "7907-7964",
      "markText": "在财富管理（投顾）领域，大模型主要应用于营销获客、客户运营、产品推介等环节，可覆盖从客户获取、留存到转化的全过程。",
      "totalCount": 2156,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300124528&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=7907&rangeEnd=7964",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/96632b50813ab9724g018e30?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=7907&rangeEnd=7964"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300124528_12_30636-30690",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "30636-30690",
      "markText": "但是，众多研究表明，GDPR设置了严格的个人信息保护标准，导致数据流通的交易成本过高，特别是对中小企业而言。",
      "totalCount": 2152,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300124528&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=30636&rangeEnd=30690",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/96632b50813ab9724g018e30?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=30636&rangeEnd=30690"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300124528_15_26407-26471",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "26407-26471",
      "markText": "由此而来的问题是，聚焦软件开发的创新通常被认为是软创新，而过去几年资本市场的投资理念在强调支持硬科技的同时对软创新重视程度不足。",
      "totalCount": 2149,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300124528&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=26407&rangeEnd=26471",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/96632b50813ab9724g018e30?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=26407&rangeEnd=26471"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300124528_6_29983-30037",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "29983-30037",
      "markText": "如果AI执行某种元任务的成本低于人工，AI将替代从事这部分元任务的劳动者，从事这部分元任务的劳动力将会减少。",
      "totalCount": 2141,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300124528&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=29983&rangeEnd=30037",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/96632b50813ab9724g018e30?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=29983&rangeEnd=30037"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300124528_5_4593-4623",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "4593-4623",
      "markText": "人才的培养推动信息产业发展，繁荣的信息产业带动人才红利显现。",
      "totalCount": 2138,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300124528&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4593&rangeEnd=4623",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/96632b50813ab9724g018e30?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4593&rangeEnd=4623"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300124528_9_45110-45163",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "45110-45163",
      "markText": "中国制造庞大的生产规模意味着可用数据的潜在规模也是非常庞大的，可支撑中国率先探索大模型与制造业的结合问题。",
      "totalCount": 2138,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300124528&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=45110&rangeEnd=45163",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/96632b50813ab9724g018e30?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=45110&rangeEnd=45163"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300124528_14_41274-41304",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "41274-41304",
      "markText": "其次，在兼顾安全的同时，在公共资金投入上可适当关注效率导向。",
      "totalCount": 2138,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300124528&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=41274&rangeEnd=41304",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/96632b50813ab9724g018e30?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=41274&rangeEnd=41304"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300124528_9_37297-37377",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "37297-37377",
      "markText": "所谓公地悲剧是指创新具有正外部性，如果没有知识产权保护制度，人人便都可以免费或者低成本地使用创新成果，由此形成的搭便车问题造成创新投入不足，不利于增进社会福利。",
      "totalCount": 2127,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300124528&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=37297&rangeEnd=37377",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/96632b50813ab9724g018e30?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=37297&rangeEnd=37377"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300124528_11_995-1035",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "995-1035",
      "markText": "在产业格局上，大模型有望升级长尾客群交互体验、形成新的服务入口/超级应用。",
      "totalCount": 2112,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300124528&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=995&rangeEnd=1035",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/96632b50813ab9724g018e30?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=995&rangeEnd=1035"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300124528_12_45485-45552",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "45485-45552",
      "markText": "AI的发展将用尽已经流通的高质量数据，我们必须让更多的数据流通聚合起来，这样才能满足AI不断增长的数据需求，增强AI领域的国际竞争力。",
      "totalCount": 2101,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300124528&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=45485&rangeEnd=45552",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/96632b50813ab9724g018e30?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=45485&rangeEnd=45552"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300124528_12_45596-45650",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "45596-45650",
      "markText": "目前，中国《数据二十条》所采取的“三权分置”方案应该说是一种暂时性的过渡措施，本质上还没有解决数据确权问题。",
      "totalCount": 2097,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300124528&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=45596&rangeEnd=45650",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/96632b50813ab9724g018e30?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=45596&rangeEnd=45650"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300124528_7_5552-5612",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "5552-5612",
      "markText": "机器能储存的知识量远超人脑，计算速度也快于人类，能够归纳海量文本和数据中的潜在规律，无疑能够高效完成人类社会的多种工作。",
      "totalCount": 2094,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300124528&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5552&rangeEnd=5612",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/96632b50813ab9724g018e30?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5552&rangeEnd=5612"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300124528_7_28950-29286",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "28950-29286",
      "markText": "我们使用前文测算的中国各职业的AI暴露度和文献估算的参数，估算了AI对劳动收入份额的潜在影响。",
      "totalCount": 2094,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300124528&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=28950&rangeEnd=29286",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/96632b50813ab9724g018e30?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=28950&rangeEnd=29286"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300124528_9_45305-45341",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "45305-45341",
      "markText": "对于追赶问题比较突出的芯片产业链等精密制造领域而言，数据问题更突出一些。",
      "totalCount": 2094,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300124528&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=45305&rangeEnd=45341",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/96632b50813ab9724g018e30?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=45305&rangeEnd=45341"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300124528_7_31886-31921",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "31886-31921",
      "markText": "以大语言模型为代表的本轮人工智能技术发展可能进一步增加灵活就业的占比。",
      "totalCount": 2086,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300124528&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=31886&rangeEnd=31921",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/96632b50813ab9724g018e30?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=31886&rangeEnd=31921"
